title: United Kingdom Imports Intra Eu - Tobacco & Manufactured Tobacco Substitutes
description: Imports Intra Eu - Tobacco & Manufactured Tobacco Substitutes in the United Kingdom decreased to 33.70 GBP Million in September from 59 GBP Million in August of 2022. Imports Intra Eu - Tobacco & Manufactured Tobacco in the United Kingdom averaged 30 GBP Million from 1996 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 168.67 GBP Million in June of 2010 and a record low of 3.54 GBP Million in February of 2022. This page includes a chart with historical data for the United Kingdom Imports of Intra EU - Tobacco & Manufactured Toba.
author: Hm Customs And Excise
